WESTERN NATIONAL INSURANCE COMPANY, Respondent,
v.
Jon NGUYEN, Appellant. A17-0314 Supreme Court of Minnesota. Dated: March 23, 2018

ORDER

Based upon all the files, records, and proceedings herein, and upon an evenly divided court,

IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the decision of the court of appeals filed on September 18, 2017, be, and the same is, affirmed without opinion.
